Class ConstraintTerm

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.umd.cs.psl.reasoner.function.ConstraintTerm

  • public class ConstraintTerm
extends java.lang.Object
    A numeric constraint. A ConstraintTerm encapsulates a FunctionTerm, a FunctionComparator, and a value. Together these define an equality or inequality statement between the value of a function and constant value.
